        <title>Data Management Plan</title>
        <description>We will design a data management plan to monitor the life cycle for all data sets that will be collected, processed or generated by the action. We will conceptualise what kind of and how data will be collected and generated and what steps will be taken to process the data. We will explain the methodologies and standards that facilitate the data management and we will outline how this data will be shared and made accessible, findable, interoperable and reusable (according to the FAIR principles), and how it will be curated and preserved. All these steps will be designed with the help of the Charit (host institution) internal data management team and will be aligned to the data management plan template from Horizon Europe.</description>
